Prerequisite has two parts: writing (prerequisite of 01:355:101, 01:355:103, or 01:355:104, or placement into 355:101 or 355:104) and math (prerequisite of 01:640:026 or placement into 640:CMA, 640:CMA, 640:PCA, 640:CLG, or 640:CLS). Common Hour Exams will be given on two (2) Tuesday nights, 7:45-9:05PM, dates TBD.
